usdEntityAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the physical and logical entity components of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdEntityAgentV1.name: usdEntityAgentV1
usdEntityAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the logical Entity component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the logical Entity component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdEntityAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Router Agent (logical entity) application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was add for the physical entity table, the physical entity contains table, and RFC 2737 enhancements to the logical entity table.

usdEntityAgentV2.name: usdEntityAgentV2
usdEntityAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the physical and logical Entity components of the
        Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the physical and
        logical Entity components is supported in the Unisphere RX 3.0 and
        subsequent system releases.
usdEntityAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the System (physical entity) and Router Agent (logical entity) applications in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
